            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Honda FREED 一直備受香港家庭車主愛戴，憑著其極高的實用性及靈活小巧的車身，是市場上其中一款最受歡迎的入門小型七人車。今日本田香港總代理合羣汽車宣佈正式引入第三代本田 FREED e:HEV ，並率先進行傳媒預覽，以下就帶大家看看新車有甚麼吸引之處！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276688" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142901-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142901-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142901-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276691" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144211-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144211-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144211-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276687" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142944-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142944-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142944-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276686" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142950-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142950-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142950-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>廠方以「Smile: Just Right Mover」理念開發新一代 FREED e:HEV，是一款適合任何年齡及性別駕駛者安心舒適地享受的七人車。新車採用了精緻簡約的設計，車頭外形非常順眼，與同廠 STEPWGN 如同出一徹，單前柱設計及門鏡位置作出了調整，A 柱位於車輪正上方，改善前方對角視野有效減少盲點，進一步提高安全性。而前排坐位改良後改改善通道空間及方便最後排乘客上落。此外，車箱採用穿透式設計，開揚無的中控台提供清晰的前方視野，車身兩側採用平坦的水平腰線，正前方的視野可延伸至車身兩旁，加上第三排特大矩形車窗，全面提高了乘坐體驗及舒適性。值得一提，新車採用左右雙電趟門設計，加上新增的中排冷氣，為乘客提供更均勻的冷氣分佈，屬同級車型中少有的功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/06-694x481.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="481" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/06-694x481.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/06-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276681" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143453-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143453-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143453-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276684" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143258-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143258-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143258-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276678" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_145458-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_145458-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_145458-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276689" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142833-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142833-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142833-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>繼承上一代 FREED 的獨特賣點，易於操控及恰到尺寸的車身大小，新車車長僅比上一代增加 45mm，並且首次加入 e:HEV 雙摩打混合動力系統，以 1.5 公升四氣缸 Atkinson 循環汽油引擎，配合 AC 同步摩打，新一代鋰離子電池及 e-CVT 組合，輸出 122 匹最大馬力及 253Nm 最大扭力。本田最新的 e:HEV 可以根據使用需要，即時智能切換不同動力模式包括: 「純電 EV 模式」大幅減少起步及低速行駛的噪音，一般情況使用的「混合動力模式」，在日常駕駛提供高效能和低油耗的平衡，以及高速行駛時使用的「引擎模式」。新車綜合油耗達到 26.5km/L（WLTP），熱效能比上一代提高 40%，引擎更加節能，進一步減低燃油成本。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143529-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143529-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143529-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276677" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/01-17-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/01-17-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/01-17-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276680" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143236-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143236-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143236-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143443-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143443-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143443-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276685" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143011-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143011-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143011-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276693" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144258-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144258-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144258-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新 FREED e:HEV 配備 HONDA 獨家的「Honda Sensing」安全及駕駛輔助系統，包括前廣角鏡頭，及前後各 8 個超聲波雷達傳感器、提供 CMBS 前方碰撞預防警示系統、RPM 道路偏離抑制系統、ACC 定速巡航系統、LKAS 車道維持輔助系統等，提供安全的駕駛體驗。首批訂單將於 2025 年 1 月交付，本田全新 FREED e:HEV 定價為 $269,880。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/011-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/011-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/011.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>HONDA FREED e:HEV 規格表:</p><p>動力: 1.5 公升 16 氣閥雙頂凸輪軸四氣缸引擎</p><p>摩打: AC 同步摩打 AC Synchronous Motor</p><p>最大馬力: 122 匹</p><p>最大扭力: 253Nm</p><p>傳動制式: e-CVT</p><p>驅動系統: 前輪驅動</p><p>耗油量: 26.5km/L</p><p>尺寸: 4310(長) x 1695(闊) x 1755(高)</p><p>售價: $269,880</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
